column4:
Expand Online Freetime Upsell: 
1. Export Freetime - Online upsell in the Bkg journey + LnS bundles; 
2. Cgnee Freetime - Post ETA upsell LnS bundles (Instant credit payments/direct debit); 
3. Automation of progressive FT pricing (linked to D&D tariff updates); 
4. Web = Maersk App features; 5. Currency calculator at M.com supports all currencies conversion (instant payments)

Optimized Freetime Pricing: 
1. Contract Freetime Pricing: system-generated pricing recommendations for Contract Freetime Extension; 
2. Replace current manual destination led ST pricing with automated sytematic solution; 
3. Optimization tool - market/competition benchmarking and patterns for pricing related to freight forecast- DTI VS FTEXT VS Tariff revenue -Xeneta/CTS commercial benchmarking.
